Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.00,0:00:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.45,0:00:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything \Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.40,0:00:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.57,0:00:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around the world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.20,0:00:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure? If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.33,0:00:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.42,0:00:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I left everything this \Nworld has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.33,0:00:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now everyone is in search of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.86,0:00:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly entered \Na Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.56,0:00:26.54,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t stand still, I can’t stop
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.56,0:00:30.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,jitto dekinai tomarenai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.52,0:00:30.50,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Daybreak hasn’t come yet and I can’t wait
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.52,0:00:34.75,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,yoake ga osokute jirettai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.77,0:00:34.75,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine four...WE GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.77,0:00:40.05,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine yon...we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.07,0:00:40.05,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Fly the flag, Break of Romance Dawn
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.07,0:00:45.56,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,hata wo ageyou Break of Romance Dawn
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.58,0:00:45.56,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Make waves, jump from your sleep
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.58,0:00:50.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,namikaze tateyou suriipu kara no janpusutaato
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.87,0:00:50.85,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to go to the unbelievable world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.87,0:00:55.44,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,arienai sekai wo iku nara
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.46,0:00:55.44,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,your toughness, that’s what it takes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.46,0:01:00.07,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,kimi no tafunesu sore ga hitsuyou
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.09,0:01:00.07,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Being brazen, is it a crime?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.09,0:01:02.91,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,medachisugi sorette tsumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.93,0:01:02.91,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanted->means Winner:D
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.93,0:01:05.91,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,shimeitehai->tsumari Winner
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.93,0:01:05.91,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Freedom is our only rule
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.93,0:01:11.46,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,jiyuu dakega ore tachi no ruuru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.48,0:01:11.46,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not our way to worry
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.48,0:01:16.92,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,shinpai nante dokofuku kaze--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.94,0:01:16.92,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,At any cost, One Piece, I’ll be the first
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.94,0:01:19.46,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ttai one piece ichibannori
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.48,0:01:19.46,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,yume miru kokoro wa choo dekai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.48,0:01:23.51,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,My dreaming heart is huge
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.53,0:01:23.51,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,samenai koto ga daiji--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.53,0:01:27.81,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s important not to wake up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.83,0:01:27.81,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,tto dekinai tomarenai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.83,0:01:30.52,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t stand still, I can’t stop
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.54,0:01:30.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,yoake ga osokute jirettai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.54,0:01:34.73,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Daybreak hasn’t come yet and I can’t wait
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.75,0:01:34.73,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine yon...we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.75,0:01:39.86,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine four...WE GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.88,0:01:39.86,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ore tachi wa...koko made kitaze
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.88,0:01:45.87,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,We...made it this far
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.89,0:01:45.87,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ore tachi wa iku...yume no arika e
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.89,0:01:48.74,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,We go...to where the dream is
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.76,0:01:48.74,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,dare mo oitekanaize--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.76,0:01:53.83,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,We won’t left anyone behind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.85,0:01:53.83,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nshin aru nomi sore ga chikai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.85,0:01:56.46,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep going forward, that’s our pledge
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.48,0:01:56.46,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,yume ga hajimatta ano hi kara
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.48,0:02:00.55,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Since the day that the dream began
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.57,0:02:00.55,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,mezasu mirai wa onaji--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.57,0:02:04.68,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,the future that I’m \Naiming at hasn’t changed
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.70,0:02:04.68,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,tto dekinai tomarenai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.70,0:02:07.30,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t stand still, I can’t stop
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.32,0:02:07.30,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,kokoro no taiyou shizumanai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.32,0:02:11.56,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,The sun of my heart will never set
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.58,0:02:11.56,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.58,0:02:15.73,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.75,0:02:15.73,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.75,0:02:19.69,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.71,0:02:19.69,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine yon...we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.71,0:02:27.71,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine four...WE GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.30,0:02:35.22,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,WE GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.24,0:02:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the pirates who are \Nafter the One Piece...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.69,0:02:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...head for the New World, the \Nsecond half of the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.09,0:02:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, no one has ever fully explored it
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.28,0:02:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,except for Gold Roger, King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.40,0:03:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The New World has ruined many \Npirates' dreams and ambitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.33,0:03:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Monkey D. Luffy,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.18,0:03:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a boy whose body turned to rubber \Nafter he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.57,0:03:08.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and his friends venture into that sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.80,0:03:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.73,0:03:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After surviving a fierce battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.15,0:03:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Straw Hats finally \Nentered the New World,--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.61,0:03:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the harshest sea ruled by the Four Emperors.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.94,0:03:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then help us!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.47,0:03:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does he mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.03,0:03:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to help us! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.34,0:03:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.56,0:03:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After being taken to a
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.99,0:03:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,mysterious facility by an \Nunknown group of people,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.43,0:03:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami and the others encountered \Nstrange children.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.95,0:03:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's help these children!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.78,0:03:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying, Nami-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.90,0:03:48.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't know for sure they need saving!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.76,0:03:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We just met them and we don't \Nknow what's going on here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.71,0:03:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not our job to help every single person!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.47,0:04:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand what you're saying but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.01,0:04:09.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you can't turn your back \Non a child crying for help!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.15,0:04:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.91,0:04:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you get away! Wait, you bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.79,0:04:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.68,0:04:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That centaur again!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.43,0:04:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.67,0:04:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The intruders are going that \Nway! Please finish them off!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.41,0:04:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the Boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.51,0:04:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see a man with swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.80,0:04:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So is that the samurai who cut our people?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.52,0:04:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Snow! Snow! I love playing with snow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.36,0:04:50.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-dah! Snowmen!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.53,0:04:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.07,0:04:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.37,0:04:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.04,0:05:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.93,0:05:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.21,0:05:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whaaat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.44,0:05:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"A Swordplay Showdown! Brook vs. \Nthe Mysterious Torso Samurai!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.17,0:05:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how far we go, all \Nwe see is a wall of ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.34,0:05:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no point in protecting ourselves \Nfrom the gas if we can't land.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.72,0:05:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give up yet. Keep searching.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.64,0:05:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.09,0:06:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An eruption?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.67,0:06:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Around here, it feels like...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.32,0:06:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...we are being watched by Akainu and Aokiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.08,0:06:21.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Oh, that's scary!\N--Let's go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.00,0:06:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.63,0:06:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.28,0:06:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.55,0:06:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.82,0:06:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare to fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.63,0:06:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.02,0:06:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Breaking the surface won't help...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.89,0:07:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a river!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.77,0:07:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey hey, that was amazing, Smo-yan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.01,0:07:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.04,0:07:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you know there was a \Nriver behind there, Smo-yan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.44,0:07:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Yeah, Smo-yan?!\N--I didn't notice it at all, Smo-yan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.57,0:07:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can tell by looking at the sea current!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.38,0:07:50.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to pay attention!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.38,0:07:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You ought to check your own behavior too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.89,0:07:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.91,0:07:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.88,0:08:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The important thing is not the \Nfact that there was a river.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.27,0:08:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is whether the ice that \Nwas blocking the river mouth
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.73,0:08:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was natural or man-made.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.19,0:08:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you mean  somebody was \Nhiding the river on purpose?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.94,0:08:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who would wanna live on such an \Nisland filled with the poison gas?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.23,0:08:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's ridiculous! No one \Nwants to live with a mask on!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.72,0:08:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the man on the Snail \Nmentioned the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.04,0:08:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You probably misheard it, Tashigi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.74,0:08:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not even a Transponder \NSnail could survive here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.87,0:08:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.19,0:08:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you have time for laughing,  \Nbreak up more ice!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.00,0:08:48.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What the hell?!\N--A wall of ice?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.01,0:08:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we collide into it,  even \Nthis warship would sink!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.19,0:08:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Oh no!\N--We gotta destroy it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.73,0:09:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.95,0:09:10.95,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,PUNK HAZARD ISLAND - THE \NMIDDLE LAKE LUFFY'S GROUP
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.79,0:09:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.21,0:09:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss! Please take care of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.30,0:09:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.45,0:09:28.16,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I, Brownbeard-sama,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.18,0:09:29.28,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,THE BOSS – BROWNBEARD - AN ALLIGATOR CENTAUR\N(A FORMER PIRATE,  BOUNTY: 80 MILLION 60 THOUSAND BERRIES)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.30,0:09:37.30,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,will kick your asses all the way to hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.47,0:09:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're all centaurs!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.11,0:09:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if they wanna join us too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.05,0:09:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure they don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.24,0:09:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're obviously prepared to fight us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.20,0:09:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're colleagues of the man who sent \Nout the emergency signal, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.29,0:09:54.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, they must be!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.16,0:09:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to clear the air \Nbefore they start to fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.81,0:09:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.18,0:10:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're here to help you \Npeople! Let's talk first!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.76,0:10:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're lying through your teeth!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.01,0:10:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're with the samurai!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.90,0:10:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So there's no doubt that you're intruders!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.02,0:10:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Samurai?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.01,0:10:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's talking about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.73,0:10:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, he's not a samurai - he's a swordsman!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.92,0:10:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a dumb meathead who picks fights \Nwithout thinking sometimes but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.70,0:10:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...he's not the one who attacked your people!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.51,0:10:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who did you call "dumb"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.87,0:10:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help! He's gonna kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.91,0:10:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I'm not gonna kill you! Stop saying that!\N--They're having a falling out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.81,0:10:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a pathetic ploy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.12,0:10:44.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't let them go any further! Shoot them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.08,0:10:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.45,0:10:59.45,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,THE ICE LANDS - INSIDE OF THE \NMYSTERIOUS FACILITY NAMI'S GROUP
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.85,0:11:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This way, kids! Run if you wanna get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.16,0:11:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're on fire, Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.78,0:11:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.98,0:11:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji entrusted me with \Nthe important mission of
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.35,0:11:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,protecting the kids and \Ngetting them out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.30,0:11:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.08,0:11:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll carry it through!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.02,0:11:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are those kids running?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.92,0:11:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a man! Leave it up to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.61,0:11:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're amazing, racoon bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.37,0:11:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a raccoon - I'm a reindeer! Hi-ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.25,0:11:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But where should we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.45,0:11:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's something you need \Nto figure out. Wachaa!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.62,0:11:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.12,0:11:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis, are we going to be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.58,0:12:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course! We've been though \Nsituations like this lots of times!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.59,0:12:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So just relax and follow us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.02,0:12:14.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.77,0:12:21.04,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,THE MYSTERIOUS FACILITY - \NBISCUIT ROOM SANJI'S GROUP
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.06,0:12:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weapons Left!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.69,0:12:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Super!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.73,0:12:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He has weapons all over his body!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.87,0:12:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the one who broke the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.75,0:12:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? You guys wanna know more about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.69,0:12:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! I'll spend as much \Ntime with you as you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.22,0:12:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Load the poison gas canisters! \NThere are no kids in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.93,0:12:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire at will!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.32,0:13:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you take off your mask \Nand smoke some poison gas with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.44,0:13:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.90,0:13:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get so mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.45,0:13:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--He ripped off our masks!\N--He broke our air tanks too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.41,0:13:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't use gas canisters!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.17,0:13:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are they?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.36,0:13:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheep?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.48,0:13:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.15,0:13:40.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This one is different from the others!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.44,0:13:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is he? He's proving an able opponent!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.58,0:13:46.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Again, what are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.77,0:13:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's what's going on with my torso!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.38,0:14:00.77,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,IN FRONT OF THE MYSTERIOUS FACILITY BROOK
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.79,0:14:03.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.71,0:14:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Wh-Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.66,0:14:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is your head and legs?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.34,0:14:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're scaring me! Please say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.35,0:14:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot! Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.69,0:14:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll reach the end of the river soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.88,0:14:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what will be there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.09,0:15:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.66,0:15:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a ghost, by any chance?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.12,0:15:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If so, you gotta obey the rules!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.25,0:15:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't come out during the day!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.70,0:15:32.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't do anything wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.73,0:15:36.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just set foot on the \Nisland to make snowmen!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.17,0:15:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, would you like to join \Nme and make one, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.90,0:15:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can make a snow sculpture as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.89,0:15:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.09,0:15:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.46,0:15:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can he attack me with such precision?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.34,0:15:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't have eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.65,0:16:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah! I don't have eyes, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.29,0:16:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scary! He's strong! Scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.84,0:16:26.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.07,0:16:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you just tell me \Nwhy you wanna fight me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.77,0:16:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aubade Coup Droit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.97,0:16:41.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two-Sword Style?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.74,0:16:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough already!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.78,0:16:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scary! Scary! Gross!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.55,0:17:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.60,0:17:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you catch the escapees?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.68,0:17:12.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I have news about G-5.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.76,0:17:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.50,0:17:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The poison gas didn't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.66,0:17:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Currently, they are breaking \Nthrough ice floes with a cannon
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.49,0:17:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and slowly forcing their way into the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.45,0:17:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll reach the laboratory in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.03,0:17:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.82,0:17:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do they want to come \Ninto the island so badly?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.61,0:17:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do they know something?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.71,0:17:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is in charge?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.07,0:17:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vice Admiral Smoker.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.02,0:18:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smoker?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.85,0:18:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of all others, that pain in the neck?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.77,0:18:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conceal all the ships moored at the front.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.04,0:18:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's gonna deal with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.91,0:18:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one's allowed to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.07,0:18:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let them find you at any cost.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.85,0:18:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you'll deal with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.34,0:18:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be ridiculous! I can't \Njust show myself like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.52,0:18:28.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there is no one else who can stop them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.01,0:18:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want me to do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.56,0:19:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We finally made it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.98,0:19:04.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I was gonna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.21,0:19:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've only just landed on the island. Get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.03,0:19:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so harsh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.15,0:19:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We did our best so be kind to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.84,0:19:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be such a baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.85,0:19:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smoker-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.48,0:19:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.76,0:19:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.17,0:19:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--There is no gas.\N--What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.47,0:19:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to believe but she's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.60,0:19:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why was there poison gas earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.29,0:19:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody who doesn't want to \Nwelcome us released it probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.76,0:20:00.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.23,0:20:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.02,0:20:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.92,0:20:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Dr. Vegapunk's laboratory.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.66,0:20:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Former laboratory, I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.37,0:20:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It should be abandoned and empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.37,0:20:25.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is still power.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.94,0:20:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is living here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.63,0:20:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Come on out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.47,0:20:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's taking you so long?! \NAre you afraid of us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.46,0:20:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have to ring a doorbell and wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.95,0:20:42.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can just break the door with \Nthe cannon of the ship, Smo-yan...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.26,0:20:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smoker-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.65,0:20:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey! Answer!\N--Just open it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.56,0:20:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.09,0:20:51.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one is allowed to be here on this island!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.66,0:20:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoever you are, you're under arrest, fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.01,0:20:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on out now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.82,0:21:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ignoring us? Okay, bring the cannon here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.04,0:21:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Let's put a big hole in it!\N--Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.29,0:21:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It opened!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.63,0:21:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you're giving up? We're the Navy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.93,0:21:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What brought you here - to my vacation home?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.13,0:21:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,White Chase-ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.10,0:21:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.05,0:21:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.34,0:21:46.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He used to be a rookie with a 440 \Nmillion berry bounty and now,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.29,0:21:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he is among them...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.30,0:21:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,..."Hawk-Eye" Mihawk, Pirate \NEmpress Boa Hancock,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.57,0:21:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and Don Quixote Doflamingo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.63,0:21:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirates backed by the World Government -
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.64,0:22:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Seven Warlords!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.28,0:22:12.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trafalgar Law!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.77,0:22:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go back, Smoker-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.84,0:22:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want anything to do with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.69,0:22:22.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know what he did!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.68,0:22:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To become a member of the Warlords...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.06,0:22:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...he delivered the hearts of one \Nhundred pirates to the headquarters!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.33,0:22:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.06,0:22:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a creep!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.61,0:22:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.76,0:22:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one, not even pirates \Nor Government allies,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.61,0:22:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is allowed to be here on this island, Law!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.47,0:23:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means you people \Nare not allowed, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.56,0:23:13.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Law stands in Smoker's way,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.21,0:23:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and neither will yield a single step.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.28,0:23:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As the situation reaches its boiling point,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.72,0:23:21.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Straw Hat Pirates suddenly \Nappear with the children in tow.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.83,0:23:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was then that Law does something that causes
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.48,0:23:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the situation to move immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.89,0:23:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.43,0:23:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"A Swordplay Showdown! Brook vs. \Nthe Mysterious Torso Samurai!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.52,0:23:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
